Options -MultiViews
RewriteEngine On

# Force HTTPS (if not already)
RewriteCond %{HTTPS} off
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301]

# Block suspicious query parameters
RewriteCond %{QUERY_STRING} ^k= [NC]
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ /$1? [R=301,L]

# Block other common spam parameters
RewriteCond %{QUERY_STRING} (utm_source=|ref=|click_id=) [NC]
RewriteCond %{HTTP_REFERER} !^https?://goevolo\.com [NC]
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ /$1? [R=301,L]

# Standard React routing
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d
RewriteRule ^ index.html [L]
```

### **Explanation:**

1. **Line 6-8**: `?k=` parameter wale URLs ko clean URL par redirect kar dega
2. **Line 10-13**: Baaki spam parameters bhi block karenge
3. **Line 15-17**: Normal React routing (without QSA flag)

